@prateekm proposed that this logic can be moved to the BEM and that we expose a retry policy independent of the consumer-implementation. I'm +1 to his proposal since it offers us significant leverage. Additionally, it seems like it's possible to do this with a minimal refactor. 

Can we make the configs of retries independent of the EventHubs and move the logic to Samza itself?

